data.description: Gorgeous Updated Home in Desirable Orcutt Location-This Single Level 3 Bedroom/2 Bath Has a Living Room AND a Family Room.  Kitchen has Been Remodeled with Granite Tile Counters, Newer Cabinetry,  Recessed Lighting & Some Newer Appliances. Both Bathrooms Have Been Updated, Primary Bathroom Has Upscale Tile Work & Walk-in Shower, Wood Laminate Flooring Throughout, Textured Ceilings and Finished Garage w/TONS of Storage.  * PLUS Airconditioning A/C*...Soft Water System & R/O. The Backyard is HUGE with Plenty of Room for an***ADU*** and Big Boy Toys, Equipped with Built-In Firepit/BBQ. Possible RV Parking ..Near Parks, Shopping and Orcutt Schools.
